Family can be anyone. We collaborated with Stefania Tejada (@stefaniatejada) to celebrate all kinds of families.

Family extends beyond relatives - it’s the people you meet throughout life that are always around to support and inspire you.

Peek behind the scenes and see how it was born.

#BeTrueToYou #FamilyDay2021 #DoWhatYouCant #Samsung

node.title: Family comes in all forms: Stefania’s Story
